      "id": "cancellation-window#cancellation-window",
      "file": "cancellation-window",
      "heading": "Cancellation Window",
      "heading_path": [
        "Cancellation Window"
      ],
      "content": "The cancellation window for orders allows customers to cancel their purchases within 24 hours, provided the order has not yet shipped. Once an order is shipped, customers are required to initiate a return instead of canceling the order.\n\n[Source: refund_policy.md#cancellation-window]",
