    {
      "id": "non-refundable-items#non-refundable-items",
      "file": "non-refundable-items",
      "heading": "Non-Refundable Items",
      "heading_path": [
        "Non-Refundable Items"
      ],
      "content": "The refund policy specifies that certain items are non-refundable, including digital gift cards, final sale items, and personalized products. Refunds for these items are only permitted if mandated by local law.\n\n[Source: refund_policy.md#non-refundable-items]",
