      "file": "refund-timeline",
      "heading": "Refund Timeline",
      "heading_path": [
        "Refund Timeline"
      ],
      "content": "Refunds that have been approved are typically processed within a timeframe of 5-7 business days. However, the specific time it takes for the refunded amount to appear in a customer's account may vary based on their bank or card provider.\n\n[Source: refund_policy.md#refund-timeline]",
