      "file": "tracking-number",
      "heading": "Tracking Number",
      "heading_path": [
        "Tracking Number"
      ],
      "content": "Customers are notified of their tracking number via email once the shipping label for their order has been generated in the warehouse. This tracking number enables them to monitor the status of their shipment during transit.\n\n[Source: shipping_faq.md#tracking-number]",
